cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to generate metaphoric paraphrases. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a novel sequence to sequence model, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Learning). The use of crowdsourcing and automatic metrics for evaluation suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence, making cs.AI another likely category. The paper also involves neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with language generation and paraphrasing, which could also fall under the category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
